### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمْ شَآقُّوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥ ۖ وَمَن يُشَآقِّ ٱللَّهَ فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ شَدِيدُ ٱلْعِقَابِ</span>

### English

This is because they defied Allah and His Messenger. And whoever defies Allah, then Allah is truly severe in punishment.